item.title: Update: Flu and More Bird Flu
item.description:
Bird Flu, Flu Season, and Protecting Your Health: What You Need to Know

While I typically focus on food and your health, pressing medical updates demand attention. Today, we’re tackling two critical topics: the latest on bird flu (avian influenza) and the rise in seasonal respiratory illnesses, including flu and COVID-19... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/forku/

item.title: Pavel Tsatsouline: Build Strength, Endurance & Flexibility at Any Age
item.description: In this episode, my guest is Pavel Tsatsouline, a world-renowned strength and conditioning coach, former military special forces training instructor, author, and founder of StrongFirst—an online school focused on “low-tech, high-concept” training to build strength for men and women of all fitness levels. Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/hubermanlab
